messages:
Name: Sofyan Amrabat
Nationality: Morocco
Date of Birth: August 21, 1996
Position: Midfielder
Current club: Real Betis
LaLiga clubs played for: Real Betis

Real Betis midfielder Sofyan Amrabat has taken part in the majority of the club's LaLiga matches in 2025/2026, making eight appearances overall and playing 601 minutes. He has been selected in the starting XI in six of these appearances across their 15 fixtures and come on as a substitute on two occasions.
Amrabat last appeared in a LaLiga game on November 23, playing 45 minutes for Real Betis against Girona in a 1-1 draw. He has been shown three yellow cards.
Real Betis next face a trip to Rayo Vallecano in LaLiga action on December 15.
Last season, Amrabat played a combined 28 Süper Lig and Serie A games between Fenerbahçe (26) and Fiorentina (2), scoring two goals and providing three assists.
Amrabat switched to Real Betis on loan in September 2025 from Fenerbahçe, for whom he has made 28 league appearances in total, scoring two goals and providing three assists.
It was on September 14, 2025 that Amrabat made his competition debut, at the age of 29 years and 24 days, versus Levante. In his LaLiga career overall, he has appeared eight times in the competition.
